com.paypal.merchant.sdk.domain
Interface CheckedInMerchantLocation

public interface CheckedInMerchantLocation

This interface returns various info about the checked in merchant. In order to take payments from checked in clients, the merchant would first need to check himself in, thus providing a location id, to which the clients within a near geo location can check into as well and make a payment.

Method Summary
